  "repo": "ibm-developer-skills-network/mcino-Introduction-to-Git-and-GitHub"
  - The original repository you're submitting the PR to
}

This proves:
✓ Your pull request is valid and open
✓ It shows your forked repository (head.repo)
✓ It shows the original repository (base.repo)
✓ It confirms the branch being merged (bug-fix-typo)
