================================================================================
TROUBLESHOOTING:
================================================================================

If curl returns empty []:
   - No pull requests exist
   - Make sure you created the PR on GitHub
   - Check that you pushed your bug-fix-typo branch
   - Wait a few moments for GitHub to process the PR

If you see "Not Found" error:
   - Check the repository URL is correct
   - Verify the repository is public
   - Check your GitHub username is correct

If jq command not found:
   - Install jq: brew install jq (Mac) or apt-get install jq (Linux)
   - Or use the alternative grep command without jq

If curl returns authentication error:
   - Add GitHub token: curl -H "Authorization: token YOUR_TOKEN" ...
   - Or use the public endpoint without authentication

